r) suggested Walmart =E2=80=94 but Amazon had a few; the only problem is th=
at I was leaving early Saturday morning on a fishing trip, and surely that =
wouldn=E2=80=99t be sufficient time for e-commerce!

In fact, it was more than enough: Amazon had delivery options of 12-4pm, 4-=
