The reason to bring this program up now is to provide some personal context=
 about the FTC=E2=80=99s latest lawsuit, this time against Amazon. Again fr=
om the Wall Street Journal ( https://www.wsj.com/articles/ftc-sues-amazon-o=
ver-manipulative-tactics-to-enroll-users-in-premium-service-85400564 ) :

The Federal Trade Commission sued Amazon.com on Wednesday, alleging the ret=
