Dark Patterns
-------------

The FTC makes two primary allegations in its complaint ( https://www.ftc.go=
v/system/files/ftc_gov/pdf/amazon-rosca-public-redacted-complaint-to_be_fil=
ed.pdf ) ; the first is about the use of =E2=80=9Cdark patterns=E2=80=9D to=
