nsual Enrollment=E2=80=9D). Specifically, Amazon used manipulative, coerciv=
e, or deceptive user-interface designs known as =E2=80=9Cdark patterns=E2=
=80=9D to trick consumers into enrolling in automatically-renewing Prime su=
bscriptions=E2=80=A6

This Hacker News thread ( https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=3D36418713 )=
