e FTC is simply anti-business.

Friction and Aggregation Theory
-------------------------------

There is a broader point to make about the question of not just dark patter=
ns, but also a number of other objectionable practices on the Internet, par=
ticularly tracking and targeting. One of the earliest Articles I wrote on S=
tratechery was called Friction ( https://stratechery.com/2013/friction?acce=
ss_token=3DeyJhbGciOiJSUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6InN0cmF0ZWNoZXJ5LnBhc3Nwb3J0Lm9ubGlu=
